Events.RelatedDescription: Closed issue "New NuGet prerelease 2.13.0-beta0001 with Office 2019 support" (#907) at OfficeDev/Open-XML-SDK
Events.RelatedBody:
This is a note that we released Beta version of SDK with support for Office 2019: namespaces and generated classes. Please give it a try and report issues, specifying NuGet package version number.

You need to check “Include prerelease” in VS NuGet Package Manager to see **2.13.0-beta0001** version.

Events.RelatedBody:
This is a note that on April 20th we released Beta 2 version of SDK with support for Office 2019: namespaces and generated classes. Please give it a try and report issues, specifying NuGet package version number.

You need to check “Include prerelease” in VS NuGet Package Manager to see 2.13.0-beta0002 version.
